{"tid":976424,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朱千雪盼似鍾楚紅保養得宜","createTime":"2019-01-10T11:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T12:15:58.000Z","uid":9573,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d3bb849c2398ac11734a42f899cd83f427deb431","tid":976424,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20190110/s00092/06ce5c3b08d1258d6bb9f44752706b5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20190110%2Fs00092%2F06ce5c3b08d1258d6bb9f44752706b5d.jpg&h=1a66e7cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝人朱千雪（Tracy）早前為韓國護膚品拍攝廣告，導演向Tracy表示要顧及實際場境和對白，起碼需要兩個分鏡來拍攝推倒骨牌及人為將骨牌停下的效果，不過Tracy希望兩個鏡頭能一齊順利進行，好讓製作團隊不用多花時間再次堆叠骨牌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190109/photo/bkn-20190109163218682-0109_00862_001_02b.jpg?20190109163354\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190109%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190109163218682-0109_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20190109163354&h=9943b2a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果，當Tracy將骨牌推倒並完成對白後，骨牌竟然自動停止倒下，一Take過完成攝錄，連工作人員都忍不住大呼Tracy是逆轉女神，其氣場令骨牌也跟着她的節奏走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190109/photo/bkn-20190109163218682-0109_00862_001_03b.jpg?20190109163354\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190109%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190109163218682-0109_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20190109163354&h=1866d784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190107/photo/bkn-20190107093128204-0107_00862_001_02b.jpg?20190107141717\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190107%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190107093128204-0107_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20190107141717&h=5396bc6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJPbC8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJPbC8p.jpg&h=151fe846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱千雪說：「講到靚，第一時間想起鍾楚紅，她永遠是超級靚的明星，保持高貴氣質，相信紅姑亦是大家的女神！」紅姑也曾為這護膚品牌拍廣告，朱千雪好興奮，希望自己10年或20年後，跟紅姑一樣保養得宜，被其他女生視為目標。"},{"pid":"b20cd6d18de550abc654937049cb7bc5e5da2fca","tid":976424,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千雪女神"},{"pid":"67771a27d1a0e4f2ee2549bc75a380ba9c5a95ec","tid":976424,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:15:58.000Z","msg":"比個死毒撚肥仔食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}